SUM with GROUP BY:

text
SELECT Department, SUM(Salary) AS TotalSalaries
FROM Employees
GROUP BY Department;
This query returns each department with the total salary for that group.

COUNT with GROUP BY:

text
SELECT Country, COUNT(*) AS NumberOfEmployees
FROM Employees
GROUP BY Country;
This finds out how many employees come from each country.

AVG with GROUP BY and WHERE:

text
SELECT Department, AVG(Salary) AS AverageSalary
FROM Employees
WHERE Status = 'Active'
GROUP BY Department;
This returns the average salary by department for only active employees.
